Package: hrvFDA
Title: Preprocessing Heart Rate Data for Functional Data Analysis
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("rj,Cook, role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for preprocessing and analyzing wearable heart rate data 
    using functional data analysis. Includes functions for assigning subject 
    IDs, validating datasets, and creating normalized time grids for irregular observations..
